    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "刘备",
        "张飞",
        "百姓甲",
        "酒保"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头戴方巾乌角，鹑衣百结褴破。足踏草鞋跟踢拖，堪叹英雄落魄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，刘备字玄德，乃大汉中山靖王之后，孝景皇帝玄孙。不幸家道冷落，父母\n早丧，一贫如洗，只落得织履为生，人人将我叫做刘穷。因此，我也就隐其真\n名不露。看天下荒荒，刀兵四起，黎民涂炭，欲想出世做一番事业，扶持社稷，\n匡救朝廷。怎奈无有进身引荐之人，以至英雄落魄，流落天涯。苍天危困英\n雄，良可叹也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘备家贫甚惨凄，\n每日里卖草鞋去东转西。\n饥寒困苦无食无衣。\n大鹏展翅冲天飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卖鞋，卖草鞋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备下。四百姓同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "百姓甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位请了。朝廷出了告条，招募军兵。我们前去看上一看。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四百姓同走圆场，同看告示。刘备上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卖了半日，一只草鞋，也未曾卖得。\n他们在这里讲些什么，待我向前问过。\n列位请了，你们在此看的是什么啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "百姓甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘穷来了，不要沾了我们一身穷气，我们快些走吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四百姓同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！这伙小人，真是气煞人也！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "燕雀安知鸿鹄志，怎识风尘一丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备上前看告示。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲人闪开，车来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽推车上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，可惜我刘备呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看那旁有一汉子，在那里自言自语，待我向前问来。\n那一汉子你在此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我呀，看榜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "粘贴榜文，为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烟尘四起，朝廷招募新兵，保卫疆土。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你便怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是国家兴亡，匹夫有责。意欲前去投军，与国家做些惊天动地之事呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀！原来是个狂生。待我走去。闲人闪开，车过来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽推车下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，这个红脸大汉，他也看不起我啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "街巷人人来谈论，\n处处百姓不安宁。\n又见城门贴榜文。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、张飞对看，同背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人仪表倒也不凡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一汉子在此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在此观榜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是招募新军之事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。唉，可惜呀，可惜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可惜何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有心投军报效，怎奈落得这样贫穷，衣衫褴褛，被人薄眼相看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听兄台之言，你我倒也志趣相同。此地不好细讲，请到三好酒楼一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备为难。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我来作东道，走，走，走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、张飞同走圆场。刘备看招牌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肆外高挂三尺布，飘来飘去招主顾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪位？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘穷，你又来赊账来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日有人请我来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁请您？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看，这是我的朋友哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你今天又算有准饭碗啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三好，你这是怎样讲话！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张大爷，我和他也是好朋友，常常说笑话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯，带路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。您二位请吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、刘备同进门，同坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您吃什么酒？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好酒取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，好酒一壶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下，上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒到，您请吃吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问兄长大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我姓刘名备，大树楼桑人氏。请问兄台尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下姓张名飞字翼德，涿州人氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦张仁兄。失敬了，失敬了。请酒，请酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闷坐店中神不定，\n沽饮几杯解烦心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三好酒楼。酒保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦，您吃酒请进吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽进门。刘备、关羽、张飞互看，同背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人仪表不凡，倒有些英雄气概。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快将好酒取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你快些取酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦，是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保取酒送给张飞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！酒保，俺要酒在先，你倒与他们先送上，莫非你这酒馆欺人不成！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！你这人好无道理，俺在这里吃酒，你在一旁大惊小怪，是何理也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！俺与酒保讲话，你在一旁答言，莫非你心中不服？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺本来不服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我劝你少管。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一定要管。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！着打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、张飞对打。刘备劝解。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要打，不要打。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、刘备对看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽、刘备",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人在哪里见过……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽同想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽、刘备",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可是那推车的那个汉子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可是那观榜的那个汉子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错。你吃酒来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是朋友，恕咱老张莽撞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。是我错了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑话了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同笑） 哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐，请坐。我们一处来饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请，我的东道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，我的东道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的东道吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说大话哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三好，快取好酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保取酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒到，我与你们三位斟上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、关羽、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请，干。哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问二位兄台尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我姓刘名备字玄德，大树楼桑人氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下张飞字翼德，涿州人氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘、张二兄，失敬了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。尊兄大名？贵乡何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟姓关名羽字云长，乃蒲州解良人氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备、张飞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关仁兄，失敬了。请问兄到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前来贸易未遂，俺意欲前去投军，与国家出力报效。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们志气相同。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，我三人志气相同，真是三生有缘。俺有意与二位兄台结为生死弟兄，不\n知二位意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也正有此心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正合我意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真巧，三人走一条路啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今天正是黄道吉日，二位兄台请到舍下。我家有一桃园，花开茂盛。我三人就\n在桃园结拜，倒也吉利。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽、刘备",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要拜府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。\n三好，命你准备乌牛白马，香烛果品，多多备些美酒佳肴，送到我家桃园，快\n去准备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张飞 （同西皮散板） 弟兄巧遇在三好，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "结拜生死患难交。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、关羽、张飞同笑，同下。）"
        }
      ],
